name: Alby #Mischief: Black -1,0
description: The 1st piece in the Alby #Mischief collection. All Alby Wistar #Mischief pieces will be 1/1. The mischief collection has no upper limit to number.  The aim of the #Mischief collection is to initiate a plague of "Uniquely Generic" Alby NFTs. New Alby #Mischief pieces will be minted by Alby Wistar periodically. Primary purchase of an original #Mischief piece will entitle the buyer to request a customised #Mischief piece to be minted (DM with @AlbyWistar).
